00:13:07.620 --> 00:13:11.081
Kung kailangan ko ng tulong, Oliva.
Itatanong ko sana agad.

00:13:11.165 --> 00:13:14.835
May mga mas kagyat na usapin sa kamay.

00:13:14.919 --> 00:13:17.463
Si Samuel ay nagkaroon ng malinaw na sandali.

00:13:18.214 --> 00:13:20.508
Dapat nating iulat ito kay Doc Anok.

00:13:24.094 --> 00:13:25.137
Patrick.

00:13:27.139 --> 00:13:28.140
Iwan mo na kami.

00:13:30.142 --> 00:13:31.143
Okay.

00:13:32.269 --> 00:13:33.354
Teka, Patrick.

00:13:35.397 --> 00:13:37.691
Lahat ng
narinig mo dito ay kumpidensyal.

00:13:39.318 --> 00:13:40.402
Naiintindihan?

