00:15:36.769 --> 00:15:39.063
Nagmumungkahi? So ikakasal ka na?

00:15:40.648 --> 00:15:43.025
Gusto ni Erika na mag-invest
sa aming publishing house.

00:15:43.108 --> 00:15:45.736
Boss V! Kahanga-hanga yan!

00:15:45.819 --> 00:15:46.946
totoo ba?

